<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>404: You Shouldn't Be Here</title>
  <style>
    @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=UnifrakturCook:wght@700&display=swap');

    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 2rem;
      background: radial-gradient(#000000, #0a0000);
      color: #e0dcdc;
      font-family: 'UnifrakturCook', cursive;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      text-align: center;
      height: 100vh;
      overflow: hidden;
      position: relative;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 4rem;
      color: #8b0000;
      text-shadow: 0 0 10px red;
      animation: flicker 1.5s infinite alternate;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    }

    p {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      max-width: 720px;
      margin: 1.2rem 0;
      line-height: 1.7;
      opacity: 0;
      animation: fadeInUp 2s ease forwards;
    }

    .glitch {
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: #444;
      margin-top: 2rem;
      white-space: nowrap;
      overflow: hidden;
      border-right: 2px solid #444;
      width: 0;
      animation: typing 3s steps(30, end) forwards, blink 0.75s step-end infinite;
    }

    .fog {
      position: absolute;
      top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; bottom: 0;
      background: url('https://www.transparenttextures.com/patterns/asfalt-dark.png');
      opacity: 0.02;
      animation: fogShift 120s linear infinite;
      z-index: -1;
    }

    a {
      color: #ff4444;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-bottom: 1px dashed #ff4444;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }

    a:hover {
      color: #fff;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #fff;
    }

    @keyframes flicker {
      0% { opacity: 0.9; text-shadow: 0 0 5px red; }
      50% { opacity: 0.6; text-shadow: 0 0 15px crimson; }
      100% { opacity: 1; text-shadow: 0 0 10px darkred; }
    }

    @keyframes fadeInUp {
      to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
    }

    @keyframes typing {
      from { width: 0; }
      to { width: 100%; }
    }

    @keyframes blink {
      50% { border-color: transparent; }
    }

    @keyframes fogShift {
      0% { background-position: 0 0; }
      100% { background-position: 1000px 0; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="fog"></div>
  <h1>Wrong Door</h1>
  <p style="animation-delay: 1s;">You weren’t meant to see this page.<br>But now that you have...</p>
  <p style="animation-delay: 2s;">The dead know your name. The Veil remembers your trespass.</p>
  <p style="animation-delay: 3s;">There is <a href="/">one way back</a>. Don’t delay.</p>
  <div class="glitch">404: You should not be here.</div>
</body>
</html>
